              "label": "AI Response",
              "body": "Good suggestion. `UpdateOperationStatusToProvisioningAsync` and `UpdateOperationStatusAsync` are structurally identical — they both construct an `AsyncOperationActivityInput` and call the same activity. The only difference is the `OperationStatusCode` value (explicit `Provisioning` vs. inferred from `Error`).\n\nI'll unify them into a single method that accepts an optional `OperationStatusCode` parameter. Same treatment for `DeleteOrchestrator`'s `UpdateOperationStatusToDeletingAsync` / `UpdateOperationStatusAsync` pair. Logging will also be consolidated."
            },
